### Predict — bridge mode
POST {{baseUrl}}/predict
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "{{sessionId}}",
  "mode": "bridge",
  "precedingText": "The average person now checks their phone over a hundred times a day, and yet "
}

###

### Predict — word mode
POST {{baseUrl}}/predict
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "{{sessionId}}",
  "mode": "word",
  "precedingText": "The economy is col"
}

